<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5887117>
    dc:description "Figs 1–13: Drusilla watanabei: male forebody (1); female forebody (2); antenna (3); male abdomen (4); male tergite VIII (5); male sternite VIII (6); median lobe of aedeagus in lateral and in ventral view (7–8); paramere (9); female tergite VIII (10); female sternite VIII (11); spermatheca in different aspects (12–13). Scale bars: 1–4: 1.0 mm; 5–11: 0.5 mm; 12–13: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5887117/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

